      <title>《行善的艺术：晚明中国的慈善事业》</title>
      <link>https://rosefinch-midsummer.github.io/zh/posts/read/%E8%A1%8C%E5%96%84%E7%9A%84%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E6%99%9A%E6%98%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%85%88%E5%96%84%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%9A/</link>
